title: Is Elijah Cummings of the United States of America (Dean Lavishley) in Italy with home Democrats?
subtitle: A number of African American legislators from the United States were part of the congressional delegation that travelled to Italy and Ghana.
author: Bethania Palma
vclaim: In July 2019, Elijah Cummings, U.S. Republic, was in Venice, Italy, with other democratic legislators.
